242
00:14:41,990 --> 00:14:43,250
Số 5 của Kamomedai.

243
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,260
A, đây.

244
00:14:46,350 --> 00:14:48,950
"Hoshiumi Korai, 169 cm"

245
00:14:48,980 --> 00:14:49,720
